<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Phoebus" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Phoebus,</orth> Apollo: <cit><quote>the sweet melodious sound that --' lute, the queen of music, makes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. pp 112" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 112</bibl></cit>. Particularly as the god of the sun: <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.3.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 3, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.2.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 2, 37</bibl> (corrupted to <emph>Phibbus</emph>). <bibl n="shak. mv 2.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 1, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.124" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 124</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.16" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 16</bibl>. * <bibl n="shak. h5 3.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III Chor.</bibl> * <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.290" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 290</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.11" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 6, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.230" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 230</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.234" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 234</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.165" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 165</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.2.114" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 2, 114</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.5.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 5, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.8.29" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 8, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.320" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 320</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 3, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.190" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 190</bibl>.
